### RAG Engine API Testing

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8001/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Root Endpoint
GET http://localhost:8001/
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Get Stats
GET http://localhost:8001/stats
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Upload Text Document
POST http://localhost:8001/upload-text
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Vidwa De Seram is the best software engineer",
  "source": "software_engineer"
}

###

### 5. Upload Another Text Document
POST http://localhost:8001/upload-text
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Company Policy: Employee Vacation Policy. All full-time employees are entitled to 15 days of paid vacation per year. Vacation requests must be submitted at least 2 weeks in advance. Vacation days cannot be carried over to the next year unless approved by management. Part-time employees receive vacation days prorated based on hours worked.",
  "source": "hr_handbook"
}

###

### 6. Simple Query
POST http://localhost:8001/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "who is the best software engineer?",
  "max_results": 3,
  "include_metadata": true,
  "similarity_threshold": 0.1
}

###

### 7. Policy Query
POST http://localhost:8001/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is our company's vacation policy?",
  "max_results": 5,
  "include_metadata": true,
  "similarity_threshold": 0.3
}

###

### 8. Complex Query
POST http://localhost:8001/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "How many vacation days do employees get and what are the requirements?",
  "max_results": 3,
  "include_metadata": false,
  "similarity_threshold": 0.3
}

